abstracts.cdata!:
The proposed project includes: (1) the
            construction and improvement of two sections of Federal
            Route I, the main highway on the West Coast of West
            Malaysia, totalling about 90 miles in length, and
            supervision by consultants; (2) consulting services for (i)
            detailed engineering of Route I and connecting roads in the
            vicinity of Kuala Lumpur, (ii) detailed engineering of about
            200 miles of roads, and (iii) town development studies for
            Kuantan and the region of North-East Negri Sembilan and an
            urban road improvement study for Kuala Lumpur.
